snippet.title: Old School Games: (KKND) Krush Kill 'N' Destroy Xtreme Game Play Part One
snippet.description: First part of me playing a Khaos mode game of KKND Xtreme. A true underdog from the "Star Craft" era. This game came out about the sametime..1997 to be exact.
